text: Bolshiye Kizeli () is a rural locality (a village) in Petropavlovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 45 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 4 km north from Petropavlovsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Bolshiye Kizeli
